<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Alfred Wright, to the tune of Amazing Grace</author>
<hymn_number>48</hymn_number>
<time_sig>8.6.8.6.</time_sig>
<title>Prayer to the Holy Spirit ƲIT48</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Shilombish Holitopa ma!
 Ish minti pulla cha,
 Hatak ilbʋsha pia ha
 Ish pi yukpalashke.

[V2]
 Pi Chu̱kʋsh nusi atukma
 Ant ish okchalashke,
 Ish pi yohbiechikbano;
 E chim aiahnishke.

[V3]
 Shilombish Holitopa ma!
 Pim anukfila hʋt
 Okhlilit kʋnia hoka,
 Ish pi on tomashke.

[V4]
 Pi chu̱kʋsh nukha̱klo yoka
 Ant pi hopohlʋchi:
 Il aiashacheka yoka
 Ish pi kashoffashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Shilombish Holitopa ma!</aka>
</song>